      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BAREFOOT RASCAL (8) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (30.39) in a Grade 6 at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Expected to feature in the finish again. SUNSET DREAM (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when eighth at this track over 600m behind Smokin' Jill (35.91) in a Restricted WIN. Leading chance. HARA'S BRIAN (1) was safely held on debut (22.94) at Q Lakeside but improved nicely to get off the mark last time winning by 2 lengths (20.32) at Capalaba. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Sure to measure up. LADY SCOTCH (3) has been in the frame at her last two runs, most recently when third (30.92) in a Grade 6 over 520m at this track.",
